Package: BioDataExplorer
Title: Interactive Biological Data Quality and Exploration Toolkit
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Your Name", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for exploring, diagnosing, and summarising 
    biological datasets. Provides automated variable type detection, missing data 
    diagnostics (including MCAR/MAR/MNAR classification), variable relationship 
    analysis, and interactive visualisation via a Shiny dashboard. Designed for 
    clinical metadata, microbiome/metagenomics data, and general tabular biological 
    data.
